                { "id": "cs-scenario-text", "type": "text", "label": "Acme Corp has 200 employees and is planning to expand into 3 new markets in Q3. The current product roadmap is overcommitted and the engineering team is at 110% capacity. Two major clients have requested custom features that conflict with the existing roadmap priorities. The VP of Product has asked you to present a resolution plan by Friday.", "fontSize": 14, "fontFamily": "var(font-sans)", "color": "#374151" }
